description: "Taking care of Breakfast" Start your day with BBA! Locally sourced, scratch-made, breakfast comfort food; on a Custom designed, top-of-the-line food Truck!!!Once upon a time, two individuals set out on an expedition to conquer a proverbial Mountain; building and creating their own breakfast food truck. Who would want to be inside of a 100 degree metal box with ovens and stoves on full-blast in the middle of the hottest city on the planet? We Do. Our oregon trail-like pioneering experience will be drawn on in the wee hours of the morning before the world awakes. Feriouciously whipping up a scratch-made breakfast; for you. So that YOU can start your day, nimble and alert, ready to summit mountain tops. Fueld by a wholesome, delicious, nourishing breakfast made of pure awesomeness. So here's to you savvy buisness consumer, go get that world, seal that deal, carpe that diem; and start your day with BBA!
name: Breakfast Burritos Anonymous
